# Real-GPU Vulkan ICDs. Previously only vulkan-virtio (the VM GPU driver) was
# installed, so on bare metal Plasma/KWin had no hardware Vulkan path. mesa
# already ships the OpenGL drivers (radeonsi/iris/etc), but shipping the Vulkan
# ICDs too gives KWin (Plasma 6.3+) and games a real accelerated path instead
# of falling back to llvmpipe (software) - which is what makes blur/transparency
# work for a while then drop out under load on real hardware.
vulkan-intel
vulkan-nouveau
vulkan-radeon
vulkan-virtio
